replies.body:
Mechanics don't equal skill. Here is the definition of it.

Skill: the ability to do something well; 

Having skill with a champion equates to how good you are with them. So your claim doesnt refute my point at all. It is incredibly hard to play Ahri well if she isn't fed in a teamfight. I wasn't entirely talking about you when I said people think she's op but I still don't think she's as strong as you said. And I pretty much explained to you why all your points are bad in my previous post (her mobility included).
